\r\n施用第二級毒品者，處三年以下有期徒刑。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e7%b0%a1%2c2744%2c20221201%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,簡,2744,20221201,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"簡","JNO":"2744","JDATE":"20221201","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}